  m_Name: ScenarioData-5
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ScenarioText: 'The Offer

    Years pass, and society remains in chaos. Mass unemployment
    has become the new normal, while governments struggle to control growing public
    anger. Companies continue relying on the same AI system that once assisted you,
    now evolved into a nearly perfect worker.


    One day, your former employer
    unexpectedly offers you your job back. They admit that maintaining a fully autonomous
    AI workforce has become more expensive than expected and invite you to return.
    The offer, however, comes with minimum wage and a lengthy employment contract
    filled with unfamiliar clauses. With your savings nearly exhausted and no other
    way to survive, you sign without reading the agreement, unaware of what is waiting
    for you when you return to the office.'
